      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i'm also looking at the ingredients on this bag i have here. it's got chicken, beef, and a bunch of stuff like sweet potato and flaxseed. do you think the fiber content matters as much as the protein for an older dog? he's been a bit sluggish lately.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
