      "role": "user",
      "content": "makes sense. i'll keep an eye on that. what about meal frequency though? i've heard some people say older dogs should eat more small meals throughout the day rather than just one big one to help with digestion and energy levels. is there a specific way i should be portioning his food given the high protein content?",
